<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Wed, 28 Jun 2023 09:35:16 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Former Apple Arcade exclusive, 'Air Twister,' is coming to PC and consoles]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>终于可以在自己选择的游戏机上玩自己喜欢的游戏了，这真是令人满足。轨道射击游戏<em>《Air Twister》</em>是最新的视频游戏， <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.iningames.com/games/air-twister/">ININ Games 宣布它将在 PS4 和 PS5、Nintendo Switch、Xbox 和 PC 上发布</a>。 <em>Air Twister</em>于 2022 年首次亮相，专为<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-apple-arcade-games-140053796.html">Apple Arcade</a>打造。 </p><div id="969229d4640641a790d1fe2b47256371"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/d-Mb7RYWXXc" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p> <em>《Air Twister》</em>是 Yu Suzuki 的创意，他设计了<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/500-run-arcade-cabinet-relives-220100636.html"><em>《Out Run</em></a> 》、 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2012-06-13-deja-review-virtua-fighter-5-final-showdown.html"><em>《Virtua Fighter》</em></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2013-12-06-segas-3d-classics-making-old-games-stand-out.html"><em>《Space Harrier》</em></a>等经典热门作品，并跟随 Arch 公主执行防止她的星球彻底毁灭的任务（<em>无压力</em>）。铃木将<em>《Air Twister》</em>归功于他在 80 年代首次想到的一款游戏，但当时的技术无法创造出来。它拥有 12 个独特的舞台和 10 个外星 Boss，其中包括一个时钟和烛台，看起来就像是<em>《美女与野兽》</em>中的场景。当您探索一系列迷你游戏并通过冒险地图解锁新挑战时，您可以选择 Boss Rush、Arcade 和 Turbo 等模式，所有这些都以荷兰作曲家 Valensia 的新歌和重新录制的歌曲为背景。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>您必须等到 11 月 10 日才能在 PC 或游戏机上帮助阿奇公主保卫她的星球免受入侵者的侵害。在此之前， <em>Air Twister</em>仍可<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-arcade-adds-20-more-games-including-an-exclusive-tmnt-co-op-title-152809631.html">在 Apple Arcade 上供 iOS 和 Mac 用户使用</a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/former-apple-arcade-exclusive-air-twister-is-coming-to-pc-and-consoles-093516795.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/former-apple-arcade-exclusive-air-twister-is-coming-to-pc-and-consoles-093516795.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 56f09bcf-d552-458e-95d4-3698edf5d306</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 09:35:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687943182</ingested><modified> 2023-06-28T09:06:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="619" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/835ffc40-158a-11ee-becf-5f7fb343b4ad" width="1100"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="619" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/835ffc40-158a-11ee-becf-5f7fb343b4