1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZSQSyQdBu43qSKTfZ4nOCuQYkRi-DMV3jU59rFwlOC_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0858MY6RT%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1">金士顿 Canvas Go Plus</a>是一个强有力的选择。它提供了我们在 CrystalDiskMark、ATTO 和 BlackMagic Disk Speed Test 测试中测试的所有卡中最高的顺序读取速度，仅略胜 SanDisk 的 Extreme 和 Nintendo Switch 品牌的卡。在我们的大文件传输测试中，它与这两张卡有效地结合在一起。它的顺序写入速度（在 CrystalDiskMark 上仅超过 100 MB/s）落后于 Pro Plus，但对于许多用途来说仍然足够快。它的随机读/写速度也仅次于三星的卡，因此它仍然是应用程序和游戏的不错选择。</p><p>这是一款 U3、V30 和 A2 级卡，并享有终身有限保修。 128GB 的​​价格为 17 美元， <a data-i13n="cpos:36;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDg1ODlSSzNNP3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8teWgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdjdqVs519PAAsqpUScBJgm-SxHbXbl-EOTfz8aG_Pjj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08589RK3M%3Fth%3D1">256GB</a>的价格通常不到 30 美元，它比 Pro Plus 稍便宜，并且与大多数具有此性能水平的卡一样实惠。不过，也有<a data-i13n="cpos:37;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYPLDf9M3dnNfwVxInhTz5LpFUiJGS52QGIYC9_fK9Ed&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0858C71LT%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26th%3D1">512GB 型号</a>可供选择，但价格通常在 60 至 70 美元之间。到那时，您应该选择我们的替代选择之一（如果它们更便宜）。</p><h2>最超值：三星 Evo Select</h2><p><core-commerce id="63ab63a44e61408b8cd13b6bfc796dde" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAetja9D2j9e49xKjupP1bt33nvUFCpJ7wkrxhnRwSWaR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09B1JFY24%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26psc%3D1">三星 Evo Select</a>比我们的首选落后一步，特别是在顺序写入速度方面（CrystalDiskMark 上的速度略低于 70 MB/s），因此它不是相机的理想选择。尽管如此，它仍然可以完美满足许多需求，并且经常在亚马逊和三星的<a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY_ttFpV8DFwwB8BSjPkeBQs383s4vIsNLGdlLYyEuA8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fcomputing%2Fmemory-storage%2Fmemory-cards%2Fevo-select-adapter-microsdxc-128gb-mb-me128ka-am%2F">在线商店</a>以便宜的价格出售。过去，我们看到其 128GB、 <a data-i13n="cpos:40;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlCMUdYTTE2L3JlZj10d2lzdGVyX0IwOVE3UTJXWjE_X2VuY29kaW5nPVVURjgmcHNjPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8teWgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAWzsRTH5vQvmDQNRFO2FHxieDUveQILn2Zo7H3hN0MsV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09B1GXM16%2Fref%3Dtwister_B09Q7Q2WZ1%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26psc%3D1">256GB</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:41;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVR_hzDXmoP-1M_b_nrfLs2LRNH_7BWon2RZNMW0jFnq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSAMSUNG-microSDXC-Expanded-MB-ME256KA-AM%2Fdp%2FB09B1HMJ9Z%2F">512GB</a>型号的售价分别低至 12 美元、18 美元和 40 美元。尽管 Evo Select 具有更高的 V30、U3 和 A2 评级，但所有这些都与经常推荐的廉价卡<a data-i13n="cpos:42;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbTg-YTHgXfFtmFnNIblEuGqR5e8zrt1HFknQpf484_j&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B7NTY2S6%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26th%3D1">SanDisk Ultra</a>相当。</p><p> Evo Select 的顺序读取速度与其宣传的峰值 130 MB/s 基本一致，这对许多人来说完全没问题。它的随机读/写性能明显落后于 Pro Plus 和 Canvas Go Plus，但与价格较高的存储卡（例如适用于 Nintendo Switch 的 SanDisk Extreme、Lexar Professional 1066x 和 SanDisk microSDXC）相当。与 Pro Plus 一样，它也享有 10 年保修。如果您只是想在一大块额外存储上节省几美元，那么这是一个很好的价值。</p><h2>另一个不错的选择：适用于 Nintendo Switch 的 SanDisk microSDXC 卡</h2><p><core-commerce id="272585d667724a7dbb425922e2a22a4a" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您发现适用<a data-i13n="cpos:43;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhWNFo0VlJZLz90aD0xJnRhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLXloLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJmNDExY2FkYS0zZjFlLTQ4N2QtOGQ5YS1jYjVkMzBjMTlmYmEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZZ6TVblclFG68ygqnFy-qJBI5ZEDsWWvEp7n_w6pf9K&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08V4Z4VRY%2F%3Fth%3D1">于 Nintendo Switch 的 SanDisk microSDXC 卡的</a>价格低于 Pro Plus 和 Canvas Go Plus，那么它是另一个值得选择的选择。在我们的基准测试中，它的顺序读取速度与金士顿卡大致相同，但其顺序写入速度稍慢（远远落后于 Pro Plus）。根据 CrystalDiskMark 的数据，它的随机读/写也落后了一步。该卡的 128GB 版本的价格通常比 Canvas Go Plus 稍高，但最近<a data-i13n="cpos:44;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhERzdGQjYxL3JlZj10d2lzdGVyX0IwQzNLWVZEV1Q_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby15aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAdsoU1vMusq-NIbHhvqB3I7gbmQjqZrl97op8KpJiFXw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08DG7FB61%2Fref%3Dtwister_B0C3KYVDWT%3Fth%3D1">512GB 版本的价格</a>已经降低了 10 美元左右。 SanDisk 还为该卡提供终身保修。请注意，我们测试了<em>Apex Legends</em>版本的 128GB 卡。 SanDisk 还销售一款<a data-i13n="cpos:45;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfuvNSDRSN61T42qx8gfcJ9ky5UP9YENcBaW5IEe01aZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07KXQX3S3%2Fref%3Dewc_pr_img_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26th%3D1"><em>超级马里奥</em>型号</a>，但我们无法透露该型号的性能如何。</p><h2>另一个不错的选择：Lexar Professional 1066x</h2><p><core-commerce id="c7b42cb1770849b59e6df97ec7bdd4c8" data-type="product-list"></p><p>同样，如果您想节省一点现金<a data-i13n="cpos:46;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhHR0NIS01ML3JlZj10d2lzdGVyX0IwQlRWTTdLNks_X2VuY29kaW5nPVVURjgmdGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby15aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAY7URpY0KNBdNfO1V0aFLfBy2xj6BvCY9XzyYdG_m_Ex&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08GGCHKML%2Fref%3Dtwister_B0BTVM7K6K%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26th%3D1">，Lexar Professional 1066x</a>是 Pro Plus 的不错替代品。这是另一款 V30、U3 和 A2 卡，与 Pro Plus 一样，在我们的基准测试中，其顺序写入速度比 Canvas Go Plus 和 SanDisk Switch 卡要快一些。这些写入速度不如 Pro Plus 快，并且其顺序读取落后于所有三张卡。随机读/写也落后于 Pro Plus 和 Canvas Go Plus，我们注意到它的速度峰值和下降在我们的文件传输测试中更加明显。不过，速度并不慢。</p><p>该卡的 128GB 和<a data-i13n="cpos:47;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhHR0NNVDJaL3JlZj10d2lzdGVyX0IwQlRWTTdLNks_X2VuY29kaW5nPVVURjgmdGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby15aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZjQxMWNhZGEtM2YxZS00ODdkLThkOWEtY2I1ZDMwYzE5ZmJhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWA0b2s6As9IKuOwTo2dGKJYl1kx3N5_MkNgbw5nYigx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08GGCMT2Z%2Fref%3Dtwister_B0BTVM7K6K%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26th%3D1">256GB 型号</a>通常售价分别为 17 美元和 22 美元。如果您想要比金士顿卡提供更好的写入速度，那么与 Pro Plus 相比，后者可能更划算。 1066x 还提供终身有限保修。</p><h2>其他著名的 microSD 卡</h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/38115180-f037-11ed-b9ff-371a217f9a97" alt="SanDisk Extreme 和 PNY Elite-X microSD 卡。" data-uuid="ceece318-0178-3bc0-a68d-be6ae7c181f0"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Jeff Dunn / Engadget</div></figure><p>我们自己没有使用它，但如果您愿意购买更强大的 UHS-II 卡，用于重型视频录制， <a data-i13n="cpos:48;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDdWNUQ4N0M3P3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8teWgtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImY0MTFjYWRhLTNmMWUtNDg3ZC04ZDlhLWNiNWQzMGMxOWZiYSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAbcfpA4y9s-U9i5HE-ZvE4fZ7okhTPkq_vUKrWlslv5A&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07V5D87C7%3Fth%3D1">Delkin Devices Power</a>已经在其他地方进行了<a data-i13n="cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://havecamerawilltravel.com/fastest-microsd-cards/">良好的测试</a>，并且应该提供比我们的卡快得多的顺序写入速度。上面选的。它是我们实际上能在库存中找到的少数 UHS-II 卡之一，但它的价格很高，起价为 55 美元，容量仅为 32GB。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:50;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:B&amp;H Photo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAY7_EXQZFUQUzUjHks0oVsOmvFyKWnjtQWvbA_eWVUrW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1692702-REG%2Fsandisk_sdsqxaa_128g_an6ma_128gb_extreme_uhs_i_microsd.html">SanDisk Extreme</a>在我们的一些顺序写入测试中与 Pro Plus 有效匹配，并提供与 Canvas Go Plus 相当的顺序读取，但这部分是因为我们只能保护该卡的 256GB 型号，该型号更高 -额定值高于 128GB 版本。它的随机性能也远远落后于三星和金士顿卡，而且通常成本更高。总体而言，最近大多数零售商的 Extreme 库存都比较不稳定。然而，如果您看到信誉良好的卖家在出售它，那么这是另一种优质选择。</p><p>与此同时， <a data-i13n="cpos:51;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Western Digital;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=92bbc6e1-f32c-4060-9f86-b3358db79a39&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Western+Digital&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARXoVmQcy_PgKUhXCekoXdgDs-C8duQS4wRPNV0kYmTL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westerndigital.com%2Fproducts%2Fmemory-cards%2Fsandisk-extreme-pro-uhs-i-microsd%23SDSQXCD-128G-GN6MA">SanDisk Extreme Pro 的</a>额定速度甚至更高（高达 200 MB/s 的顺序读取），但截至撰写本文时，大多数值得信赖的零售商似乎都无法提供该产品。</p><p>在 CrystalDiskMark 中， <a data-i13n="cpos:52;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaWDG_XP7aqt5Teb8HTtGJKRjEmauhU-xuutsPebK_E4&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPNY-Elite-X-Micro-128GB-Class%2Fdp%2FB07KNTXKL3">PNY Elite-X 的</a>随机读/写性能与 Pro Plus 和 Canvas Go Plus 相差不远，而且它通常价格便宜，但在我们的顺序测试中远远落后。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-microsd-card-130038282.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-microsd-card-130038282.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f411cada-3f1e-487d-8d9a-cb5d30c19fba</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 20:20:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687915945</ingested><modified> 2023-06-28T01:32:43+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="1173" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/4f77aa60-f3eb-11ed-9d5f-fe3fdd8ad1ed" width="1953"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:descri