ll-be-able-to-use-tesla-superchargers-starting-in-2024-141546633.html">里维安</a></ins>所有人都宣布计划采用 NACS。反过来，这促使德克萨斯州等州强制政府资助的电动汽车充电站配备特斯拉的连接器。随着 NACS 背后的势头不断增长，持反对态度的人如<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/electrify-america-10000-chargers-us-canada-by-2026-140040719.html">使美国电气化</a></ins>可能会重新考虑他们对连接器的立场。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/the-sae-is-creating-a-standardized-version-of-teslas-ev-charging-plug-175233691.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-sae-is-creating-a-standardized-version-of-teslas-ev-charging-plug-175233691.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> eb8c8880-4f14-4708-b5d8-26438d36ef5c</guid><dc:creator>伊戈尔·博尼法西奇</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 17:52:33 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687916038</ingested><modified> 2023-06-28T01:34:04+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Igor Bonifacic]]></category><media:content height="3826" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/0faec290-1512-11ee-be7c-8f5d334153d8" width="5740"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3826" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/0faec290-1512-11ee-be7c-8f5d334153d8" width="5740"><media:med